  <li>Repairs.</li>
  <li>Supplies.</li>
  <li>Taxes.</li>
  <li>Utilities.</li>
  <li>HomeOwner Association (HOA) fees.</li>
  <li>FIRST YEAR RENTAL: Rental starting date (MM/DD/YYYY).</li>
  <li>FIRST YEAR RENTAL: Closing document.</li>
  <li>FIRST YEAR RENTAL: Term of loan (e.g. 15 years, 30 years).</li>
  <li>FIRST YEAR RENTAL: Land value near the rental starting date from the county website.</li>
  <li>MIXED (RENTAL AND PRIMARY RESIDENT TOGETHER): Rental ratio.</li>
  <li>PARTIAL YEAR AND MIXED: Specify expenses for what time period, for what space (entire house or the rental rooms).</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="homeowner-and-itemizing-items">Homeowner and itemizing items</h3>

